<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-08-24T17:36:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-08-24T17:36:00-05:00" n="1081" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1081">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.512/1363</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Special Representative <persName type="from">Rodgers</persName> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                    State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Extract]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico City</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-08-24T16:00:00-06:36">
                                    <hi rend="italic">August 24 1916, 4 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>314. Department’s 316 August 23, 7 p.m. Cabrera informed me definitely
                            this morning that there would be no extension time payment without
                            penalty mining taxes for last tercio, this decision which he considered
                            final being for reasons communicated to me yesterday and incorporated in
                            my 208. Have no reason to believe there will be alteration this program
                            at present.</p>
                        <p>Two months grace with penalty twenty-five per cent September and perhaps
                            fifty per cent October will be granted according to present plan.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Rodgers</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>